| File | Location | Change |
|---|---|---|
| `ConstPropVisitor.java` | `getIdValue` (lines 62-74) | Remove hardcoded `"result"` debug checks; add missing `return` statements |
| `ConstPropVisitor.java` | Add new method | Add `collectCallSiteArgValues` which `InterConstPropVisitor` calls |
| `InterConstPropVisitor.java` | `buildTopoOrder` (~line 130) | Uncomment `Collections.reverse(result)` |
| `DeadCodeVisitor.java` | `addIfLive` (lines 570-577) | Remove the dead `else { if (varName.equals("result")) ; }` block |
